      "text": [
        ": قُلْتُ لَهُ إِذَا كَانَتِ اَلْحُرَّةُ تَحْتَ اَلْعَبْدِ كَمْ يُطَلِّقُهَا فَقَالَ \"قَالَ عَلِيٌّ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ \"اَلطَّلاَقُ وَ اَلْعِدَّةُ بِالنِّسَاءِ \" \"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4863 - Ḥammad ibn ʿIsa narrated from Abu Abdullah (as), who said:\nI asked him, \"If a free woman is married to a slave, how many divorces can he pronounce against her?\"\nHe (as) replied: \"Ali (as) said: 'Divorce and the waiting period (ʿiddah) are determined according to the status of the women.'\""
        ]
      }
    },
